        <Param val="This experiment consists of three parts:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;1. First, you will be trained and tested on regular videos of human actions.&amp;#10;2. Then, you will see videos of the same actions, where texture and shape information have been removed.&amp;#10;3. Finally, you will see videos of the same actions without texture and shape, and with background flickering added.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In each part, your task is to identify the action shown in each video by selecting one of five categories.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;We will record your response accuracy and reaction time for every video.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Press the SPACEBAR to begin.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;" valType="str" updates="constant" name="text"/>
